131 6.58729 13 6.05895 13 5.5C13 3.567 14.567 2 16.5 2ZM16.5 16.5C15.3954 16.5 14.5 17.3954 14.5 18.5C14.5 19.6046 15.3954 20.5 16.5 20.5C17.6046 20.5 18.5 19.6046 18.5 18.5C18.5 17.3954 17.6046 16.5 16.5 16.5ZM7.5 10C6.39543 10 5.5 10.8954 5.5 12C5.5 13.1046 6.39543 14 7.5 14C8.60457 14 9.5 13.1046 9.5 12C9.5 10.8954 8.60457 10 7.5 10ZM16.5 3.5C15.3954 3.5 14.5 4.39543 14.5 5.5C14.5 6.60457 15.3954 7.5 16.5 7.5C17.6046 7.5 18.5 6.60457 18.5 5.5C18.5 4.39543 17.6046 3.5 16.5 3.5Z"></path></svg></i></span></button></div></div></div><div class="BookPageMetadataSection"><div class="BookPageMetadataSection__contributor"><h3 class="Text Text__title3 Text__regular" aria-label="List of contributors"><div class="ContributorLinksList"><a class="ContributorLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/145435.Kentaro_Miura"><span class="ContributorLink__name" data-testid="name">Kentaro Miura</span></a>, <a class="ContributorLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/241687.Jason_DeAngelis"><span class="ContributorLink__name" data-testid="name">Jason DeAngelis</span><span data-testid="role" class="ContributorLink__role"> (<!-- -->Translator<!-- -->)</span></a></div></h3></div><div class="BookPageMetadataSection__ratingStats"><a class="RatingStatistics RatingStatistics__interactive" href="#CommunityReviews" aria-label="Rating statistics"><div class="RatingStatistics__column" aria-label="Average rating of 4.44 stars" role="figure"><span aria-hidden="true"><span aria-label="Rating 4.44 out of 5" role="img" class="RatingStars RatingStars__medium"><span class="RatingStar RatingStar--medium"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="presentation"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><path class="RatingStar__fill" d="M12.4770229,1.34326985 L15.0891563,9.1315756 L23.4968842,9.1315756 C23.7747474,9.1315756 24,9.35682823 24,9.63469143 C24,9.79809886 23.9206399,9.95132779 23.7871766,10.0456121 L16.9959586,14.8432273 L19.5982827,22.6117477 C19.6865419,22.875221